  "response": "Here are some of the best punchline jokes that always get a laugh:\n\n1. **Why don\u2019t skeletons fight each other?**  \n   *They don\u2019t have the guts.*\n\n2. **Why did the scarecrow win an award?**  \n   *Because he was outstanding in his field.*\n\n3. **Why don\u2019t scientists trust atoms?**  \n   *Because they make up everything.*\n\n4. **What do you call fake spaghetti?**  \n   *An impasta.*\n\n5. **Why did the math book look sad?**  \n   *Because it had too many problems.*\n\n6. **What do you call cheese that isn\u2019t yours?**  \n   *Nacho cheese.*\n\n7. **Why can\u2019t you give Elsa a balloon?**  \n   *Because she\u2019ll let it go.*\n\n8. **What do you get when you cross a snowman and a vampire?**  \n   *Frostbite.*\n\n9. **Why don\u2019t eggs tell jokes?**  \n   *Because they might crack up.*\n\n10. **What\u2019s orange and sounds like a parrot?**  \n    *A carrot.*\n\nLet me know if you need more\u2014I\u2019ve got plenty! \ud83d\ude04",
